OL,3,CFire crews tackle blaze at recycling
OL,4,Ccentre
OL,6,FFirefighters are continuing to tackle
OL,7,Fa fire at a waste recycling centre
OL,8,Fnear Belfast.
OL,10,FA Northern Ireland Fire and Rescue
OL,11,FService (NIFRS) spokesperson said five
OL,12,Fappliances were at the scene on
OL,13,FHillsborough Road in Carryduff on
OL,14,FMonday morning.
OL,16,FCrews were sent to the incident on the
OL,17,FHillsborough Road about 8.45am on
OL,18,FSunday. At its height 10 crews were
OL,19,Ftackling the blaze which is at a
OL,20,Fwarehouse full of recycling material.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/3
