OL,3,CFire crews tackle blaze at recycling
OL,4,Ccentre
OL,6,FThey have advised local residents to
OL,7,Fkeep windows and doors closed and
OL,8,Fasked members of the public to avoid
OL,9,Fthe area to help with the firefighting
OL,10,Foperation.
OL,12,FSouth Belfast MLA Kate Nicholl posted
OL,13,Fon X and said it was "very concerning
OL,14,Fto see images of Irish waste facility
OL,15,Fon fire in Carryduff ` massive blaze,
OL,16,Fthoughts with the fire brigade who are
OL,17,Fdealing with it right now".
